data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome Home to Effortless Living! This dazzling updated 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom townhome, enveloped in the serenity of a gated, pet-friendly community where your ease and convenience take center stage! Spanning a comfortable 1,110 sq ft, every inch of this home exudes warmth and modern elegance. Nestled in a maintenance-free community, say goodbye to yard work and exterior upkeep, all are seamlessly managed for you. The community's lush landscaping, matched with the perfect location near stores, restaurants, and various entertainment options, makes life not just convenient but extraordinarily delightful. Enjoy potential ease in your daily travels with quick and easy access to major roadways. The brand-new Air Conditioning Unit, coupled with the cutting-edge Nest Smart Thermostat technology, ensures your home is always at the perfect, cost-efficient temperature. The home’s thoughtful design optimizes space and comfort, promising a cozy retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. In this digital age, stay effortlessly connected with high-speed internet and cable. With water, sewer, and trash also included in the Homeowners Association fees, bask in the simplicity of all-inclusive living. ADDITIONAL FEATURES: Pet-Friendly Community: Your furry friends will feel right at home! Premium Location: Have every convenience at your fingertips! Close to Westfield Mall, Regency & I-75. A Brand-New Air-Conditioning Unit: Stay cool all year round! Nest Smart Thermostat: Modern, efficient, and convenient! Home is currently vacant but has been virtually staged for potential home buyers to visualize and give you ideas to furnish to your liking. Schedule your showing today!
